Title: Europe Is in Danger of Regulating Its Tech Market Out of Existence
Description: Poorly designed laws are forcing global firms to leave.

Title: Simple Messaging in .NET With Redis Pub/Sub
Description: Redis is a popular choice for caching data, but its capabilities go far beyond that. One of its lesser-known features is Pub/Sub support. Redis channels offer an interesting approach for implementing real-time messaging in your .NET applications.
